#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:2
msgid "上下文和流式消息管理"
msgstr "Context and Streaming Message Management"

#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:5
msgid "获取上下文环境"
msgstr "Obtain context environment"

#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:7
msgid "图引擎运行的过程中，每个节点以及 :py:class:`~evofabric.core.tool.ToolManager` 调用的工具，都会有独立的上下文环境 :py:class:`~evofabric.core.graph.StreamCtx`，可以通过调用 :py:meth:`~evofabric.core.graph.current_ctx` 来获取。"
msgstr "During the operation of the graph engine, each node as well as the tools called by :py:class:`~evofabric.core.tool.ToolManager` will have an independent context environment :py:class:`~evofabric.core.graph.StreamCtx`, which can be obtained by calling :py:meth:`~evofabric.core.graph.current_ctx`."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:9
msgid "上下文环境包括："
msgstr "Contextual environment includes:"

#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:11
msgid "node_name: 当前节点名字。"
msgstr "node_name: Current node name."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:13
msgid "call_id: 节点运行时生成的唯一 UUID。同一节点不同运行轮次时，ID不同。"
msgstr "call_id: A unique UUID generated at node runtime. The ID is different for the same node in different run rounds."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:15
msgid "tool_name: 当前执行的工具名。"
msgstr "tool_name: the name of the currently executing tool."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:17
msgid "tool_call_id: 工具执行ID。对应大语言模型输出的 :py:class:`~evofabric.core.typing.ToolCall` 中 ``id`` 。"
msgstr "tool_call_id: Tool Execution ID. Corresponds to the ``id`` in the :py:class:`~evofabric.core.typing.ToolCall` class of the large language model's output."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:19
msgid "在节点中获取上下文信息："
msgstr "Obtain context information in the node:"

#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:33
msgid "管理流式消息"
msgstr "Manage Streaming Messages"

#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:35
msgid "我们支持通过 :py:meth:`~evofabric.core.graph.set_streaming_handler` 注册自定义的流式消息 Handler 来处理节点输出的流式消息。"
msgstr "We support registering custom streaming message Handlers via :py:meth:`~evofabric.core.graph.set_streaming_handler` to process streaming messages from node outputs."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/graph/ctx_and_streaming.rst:37
msgid "流式消息输出是 ``dict`` 格式，包含上下文环境和一个 ``payload`` 字段，``payload`` 的值即为节点通过 :py:meth:`~evofabric.core.graph.StreamWriter.put` 方法传出流式消息。"
msgstr "Streaming message output is in ``dict`` format, containing the context environment and a ``payload`` field, where the value of ``payload`` is the streaming message output by the node through the :py:meth:`~evofabric.core.graph.StreamWriter.put` method."

